OL,3,CTeenager rescued after being stuck
OL,4,Cpartway down a cliff
OL,6,FA teenage boy was rescued from the
OL,7,Fcliffs at Soldiers Bay in Guernsey
OL,8,Fyesterday evening (Saturday 28 March)
OL,9,Fafter he got stuck partway down the
OL,10,Fcliffs.
OL,12,FThe 17-year-old boy was stranded after
OL,13,Fhe was unable to move to safety.
OL,15,FGuernsey's police, Fire and Rescue,
OL,16,FCliff Rescue Team and Coastguard
OL,17,Freceived the call about the incident
OL,18,Fat around 5:20pm.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
