OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1774793495
OL,3,CTeenager rescued after being stuck
OL,4,Cpartway down a cliff
OL,6,FThe stranded teenager was located with
OL,7,Fa drone and brought safely down to the
OL,8,Fbottom of the cliff using a rope.
OL,10,FHe was then taken to St Peter Port
OL,11,FHarbour on the RNLI's Inshore lifeboat
OL,12,Fat around 7:20pm, where he was
OL,13,Fassessed and found to have no injuries.
OL,15,FGuernsey's Assistant Harbour Master,
OL,16,FMike Harris, says: "This operation
OL,17,Fdemonstrated excellent cooperation
OL,18,Fbetween all emergency services
OL,19,Finvolved.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
