OL,3,CTeenager rescued after being stuck
OL,4,Cpartway down a cliff
OL,6,F"The location presented significant
OL,7,Fchallenges, and we commend the swift,
OL,8,Fprofessional actions of Guernsey Fire
OL,9,F& Rescue, Police and the RNLI Lifeboat
OL,10,Fcrew."
